item.title: King County Fire Chiefâ€™s Issue STAGE 1 (Restrictions) Burn Ban
item.description: Effective Thursday June 1st at 0800hrs the King County Fire Chief’s Association, King County Fire Marshals Association and the King County Fire Marshal are implementing a STAGE 1 (burn restrictions) Ban.  This ban specifically relates to yard debris/residential burning.
